Package: ybarojs-debian
Version: 1.0.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: ybaroj <ybaroj@localhost>
Depends: sudo, git, iwd, sway, waybar, tofi, greetd, wlgreet, fonts-jetbrains-mono, fonts-noto-core, wireplumber, pipewire-pulse, unzip
Replaces: sway, waybar, tofi, greetd, wlgreet
Conflicts: fonts-font-awesome
Description: Sway window manager meta-package with Catppuccin theme
 Meta-package providing a complete Wayland desktop environment
 based on the Sway tiling window manager with Catppuccin Mocha
 theming (blue/mauve/pink/green accents).
 .
  Features include:
  - Waybar status bar with Catppuccin Mocha theme
  - Git version control system
  - iwd wireless networking daemon with auto-enable
  - impala WiFi management tool (TUI for iwd)
  - Tofi application launcher
  - Greetd display manager with wlgreet and themed login
  - System-wide configuration in /etc/xdg/ and /etc/greetd/
  - Automatic JetBrainsMono Nerd Font installation
  - Interactive sudo user setup during installation
  - _greetd user configured for GPU and input device access
  - Optional colored bash prompt configuration help
